MinNOC_CSF1PO: Minimal NOC (allele count / 2, rounded up) at CSF1PO
MinNOC_D16S539: Minimal NOC (allele count / 2, rounded up) at D16S539
PercAF_D1S1656: Percentage of alleles at D1S1656 present in the population database
MinNOC_Penta D: Minimal NOC (allele count / 2, rounded up) at Penta D
MinNOC_Penta E: Minimal NOC (allele count / 2, rounded up) at Penta E
SumAF_TH01: Sum of frequencies of the alleles at TH01 defined in the population database
MinNOC_TPOX: Minimal NOC (allele count / 2, rounded up) at TPOX
stdHeight_vWA: Variation (standard deviation) of peak heights at vWA
stdAllele: Variation (standard deviation) of the number of alleles per locus
MAC5-6: Number of loci with 5 or 6 alleles
peaksBelowRFU: Number of peaks below the stochastic threshold of 800 RFU
MatchKans: Probability of a random Dutch person matching to this DNA profile
